long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Float into Chrome with Astronaut in Outer Space live wallpapers, plus a search bar and quick-access icons for cosmic browsing.

Embark on a cosmic journey with the Astronaut in Outer Space Live Wallpaper extension for Chrome! Each new tab transports you to the stunning, silent beauty of the universe, with live wallpapers featuring a lone astronaut drifting among the stars and planets. These high-definition visuals capture the vastness and wonder of space, perfect for those who dream of exploration and discovery.

Beyond the mesmerizing scenery, this extension includes a built-in Google search bar for effortless browsing and customizable quick-access icons to your favorite websites. With a blend of functionality and breathtaking visuals, this extension lets you stay connected to the web while immersing yourself in the mysteries of space.

Perfect for space enthusiasts, sci-fi fans, and those who appreciate the calm of the cosmos, the Astronaut in Outer Space Live Wallpaper extension transforms each new tab into a window to the stars. Every time you open a new tab, feel the infinite vastness of space inspiring your online journey!
